HARARE - Congolese chanter and Utakataka Express member Gift &ldquo;Shiga Shiga&rdquo; Katulika will unveil his second solo studio album Basa Ndakapihwa which features controversial Zimdancehall artiste Soul Jah Love on Wednesday at City Sports Bar in the capital, Harare. Katulika, who is a rhumba and sungura artiste, said the fusion of the genre with Soul Jah Love&rsquo;s dancehall style brings a rare combination that will impress the audience.